---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Get in touch
intro: "Here's how to contact Scoonie Medical Practice."
description: "Contact details for Scoonie Medical Practice — phone number, email address, location, and how to find us."
breadcrumb:
  - label: Contact
    url: /contact/
  - label: Get in touch
---

<div class="max-w-3xl">

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">

    <div class="contact-block">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark mb-3">Phone</h2>
      <div class="contact-block__item">
        <svg class="contact-block__icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p><a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}" class="text-brand-primary font-semibold text-lg">{{ site.phone }}</a></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">Monday – Friday, 08:00 – 18:00</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-block__item mt-3">
        <svg class="contact-block__icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.25 9.75v-4.5m0 4.5h4.5m-4.5 0l6-6m-3 18c-8.284 0-15-6.716-15-15V4.5A2.25 2.25 0 014.5 2.25h1.372c.516 0 .966.351 1.091.852l1.106 4.423c.11.44-.054.902-.417 1.173l-1.293.97a1.125 1.125 0 00-.38 1.21 12.035 12.035 0 007.143 7.143c.441.162.928-.004 1.21-.38l.97-1.293a1.125 1.125 0 011.173-.417l4.423 1.106c.5.125.852.575.852 1.091V19.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-2.25z"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">For urgent help when we're closed:</p>
          <p><a href="tel:111" class="text-brand-primary font-semibold">NHS 24 — 111</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-block">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark mb-3">Email</h2>
      <div class="contact-block__item">
        <svg class="contact-block__icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p><a href="#" data-email="{{ site.email | replace('@', '|') }}" class="text-brand-primary obfuscated-email">Loading...</a></p>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid mt-1">We aim to respond to emails within 2 working days. Please do not email urgent medical queries.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="contact-block mb-8">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark mb-3">Visit us</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="contact-block__item">
        <svg class="contact-block__icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z"/>
        </svg>
        <address class="not-italic text-sm">
          <strong>{{ site.address.line1 }}</strong><br>
          {{ site.address.line2 }}<br>
          {{ site.address.town }}<br>
          {{ site.address.county }}<br>
          {{ site.address.postcode }}
        </address>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">
        <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-neutral-dark">Parking</strong><br>Free patient parking is available at Leven Health Centre.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-neutral-dark">Bus</strong><br>Several bus routes serve Leven. Check <a href="https://www.travelinescotland.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Traveline Scotland</a> for the latest timetables.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {# ── MAP ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark mb-3">Find us</h2>
    <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-gray-200">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.openstreetmap.org/export/embed.html?bbox=-2.998%2C56.193%2C-2.985%2C56.199&layer=mapnik&marker=56.196%2C-2.9915"
        width="100%"
        height="300"
        style="border:0;"
        loading="lazy"
        title="Map showing the location of Leven Health Centre"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid mt-2">
      <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Leven+Health+Centre+Victoria+Road+Leven+Fife" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-primary">Get directions on Google Maps →</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  {# ── CONTACT FORM ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div class="contact-block mb-8">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark mb-3">Send us a message</h2>
    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded p-3 mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-dark">
      <strong>Do not use this form for urgent medical queries.</strong> If you need urgent help, call us on <a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}" class="text-brand-primary font-semibold">{{ site.phone }}</a> or NHS 24 on <a href="tel:111" class="text-brand-primary font-semibold">111</a>.
    </div>
    <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" class="space-y-4">
      <p class="hidden">
        <label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field"></label>
      </p>
      <div>
        <label for="contact-name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-dark mb-1">Name <span class="text-red-600">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-brand-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-primary">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="contact-dob" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-dark mb-1">Date of birth <span class="text-neutral-mid">(optional)</span></label>
        <input type="date" id="contact-dob" name="dob" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-brand-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-primary">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="contact-email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-dark mb-1">Email or phone number <span class="text-red-600">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" id="contact-email" name="contact" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-brand-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-primary">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="contact-category" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-dark mb-1">Category</label>
        <select id="contact-category" name="category" class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-brand-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-primary">
          <option value="general">General enquiry</option>
          <option value="prescription">Prescription query</option>
          <option value="letter">Letter or form request</option>
          <option value="registration">Registration question</option>
          <option value="feedback">Feedback</option>
          <option value="other">Other</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="contact-message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-dark mb-1">Message <span class="text-red-600">*</span></label>
        <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="5" required class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:border-brand-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-brand-primary"></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Send message</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div class="prose-content">
    <h2>BSL users</h2>
    <p>If you use British Sign Language, you can contact us using the <a href="{{ site.bslLink }}" rel="noopener noreferrer">ContactSCOTLAND BSL video relay service</a>.</p>

    <h2>Information in other languages</h2>
    <p>NHS Inform provides health information in <a href="https://www.nhsinform.scot/translations/" rel="noopener noreferrer">multiple languages</a>. If you need an interpreter for your appointment, please let us know when booking and we will arrange this.</p>
    <p>If you have medical records or documents in a language other than English, we require an official English translation before they can be reviewed by our clinical team.</p>

    <h2>Accessibility</h2>
    <p>Leven Health Centre has step-free access, accessible toilet facilities, and a hearing loop. If you have any access requirements, please let our reception team know when booking your appointment.</p>
  </div>

</div>
